universum.studios.websocket.adapter

Interface WebSocketDelegate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseWebSocketDelegate

    public interface WebSocketDelegate
    An interface that is used to hide a concrete implementation of WebSocket for purpose of adapting an asynchronous nature of WebSocket to synchronous nature of standard Socket using WebSocketAdapter.
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  WebSocketDelegate.Frame
      Basic interface for WebSocket frame.
      static interface  WebSocketDelegate.OnConnectionListener
      Listener which may be used to listen for callbacks about connected and disconnected WebSocket.
      static interface  WebSocketDelegate.OnIncomingFrameListener
      Listener which may be used to listen for callback about received WebSocket frame.
